body.p: The following Norsemen bought or sold real estate in Chicago during the past week:
C. W. Johnson to J. LeBrun: Read Court, corner of Iowa Street. Price, $2,000.
C. A. Anderson to Catherine Loftus: Lakeside Terrace, south of Howard Avenue. Price, $8,000.
M. Barteine to J.J. Benson: Newgard Avenue, south of Hayes Avenue. Price, $1,200.
J. Oliver to Ole E. Strand: Cornelia Avenue, west of Herndon Street. Price, $1,500.
C. O'Shannesay to Ludvig Toresen: Humboldt Avenue, east of Kimball Avenue. PRice, $1,600.
B. Ardenghe to Nels O. Larsen: Curtis Avenue, south of 113th Avenue. Prive, $1,300.
G. Nelson to N. Bodevin: 56th Street, west of Union Avenue. Price, $4,100.
H. A. Hansen to John Bain: Justine Street, north of 62nd Street. Price, $5,500.
E. A. Scott to Frank Carlson: Aberdeen Street, north fo 66th Street. Price, $7,000.
Ralph Ware to Carl Hansen: 67th Street and 44th Avenue. Price, $42,00.
S. C. Lundgren to Peter Rasmussen: Elizabeth Street, north of 63rd Street. Price, $2,200.
